!                    |                                                 |
! NAME               | DESCRIPTION                                     |
!--------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
! mcsph1             | 3D Markov chain                                 |
! difut1             | horizontal diffusion u-tendency                 |
! difvt1             | horizontal diffusion v-tendency                 |
! ugwdt1             | gravity wave         u-tendency                 |
! vgwdt1             | gravity wave         v-tendency                 |
